Description: A Bayesian approach to geometric extreme value analysis based on: Papastathopoulos, I., De Monte, L., Campbell, R. and Rue, L. (2023) 'Statistical inference for radially-stable generalized Pareto distributions and return level-sets in geometric extremes', arXiv preprint.
